### Get recipe detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes/{{recipeId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get original uploaded image
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipe/{{recipeId}}/original/1
Accept: image/*

### Get hero image placeholder response
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipe/{{recipeId}}/hero
